    {
      "id": "PopularPost361090",
      "post_content": "Yes, your opponent may guess it could be coming a turn or two away, but that doesn't really change things. They can also guess it's coming if they know you're playing a discard deck as well. And their reactions aren't any better. You cast Duress, they can still respond with an instant to try to clear their hand first.  \n  \nWith this, you can trigger heroic in response to their casting a spell. If that's their only card, you've effectively countered it since they have to discard it before it's cast.  \n  \nAnd the 1/3 body is significant. He's out of ping damage range and can even bounce a 2/2 in combat. Not a lot of downside here.",
      "posted_by": "RedJaron",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost361090\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">Yes, your opponent may guess it could be coming a turn or two away, but that doesn't really change things.  They can also guess it's coming if they know you're playing a discard deck as well.  And their reactions aren't any better.  You cast Duress, they can still respond with an instant to try to clear their hand first.<br/><br/>With this, you can trigger heroic in response to their casting a spell.  If that's their only card, you've effectively countered it since they have to discard it before it's cast.<br/><br/>And the 1/3 body is significant.  He's out of ping damage range and can even bounce a 2/2 in combat.  Not a lot of downside here.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '361090'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy76650\">RedJaron</span>\r\n                                (1/31/2014 3:54:46 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_pos