    {
      "id": "PopularPost361879",
      "post_content": "If your opponent empties their hand just because this guy hit the field, that's not all that bad. My favorite position in a game is when my opponent is top-decking, and I'm slowly regaining control of the board by pacing myself with my spells. It feels good to have 3 or 4 cards when my opponent has none. It also forces them to play whatever they draw, since they know it can be discarded at any time you choose, effectively locking them in top-deck mode. The text, \"Whenever you cast a spell that targets Ashiok's Adept, each opponent discards a card\", doesn't just do what it says. It's a mind game as well, and you can't overlook that. The 1/3 body is pretty nice too. There are quite a few 2 power creatures in BotG that can clog up the board early. This card seems like it was carefully crafted, and I like that.  \n  \n3/5",
      "posted_by": "StreamHopper",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost361879\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\">If your opponent empties their hand just because this guy hit the field, that's not all that bad. My favorite position in a game is when my opponent is top-decking, and I'm slowly regaining control of the board by pacing myself with my spells. It feels good to have 3 or 4 cards when my opponent has none. It also forces them to play whatever they draw, since they know it can be discarded at any time you choose, effectively locking them in top-deck mode. The text, \"Whenever you cast a spell that targets Ashiok's Adept, each opponent discards a card\", doesn't just do what it says. It's a mind game as well, and you can't overlook that. The 1/3 body is pretty nice too. There are quite a few 2 power creatures in BotG that can clog up the board early. This card seems like it was carefully crafted, and I like that.<br/><br/>3/5</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '361879'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy16408\">StreamHopper</span>\r\n                                (2/4/2014 9:50:15 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    