    {
      "id": "PopularPost369951",
      "post_content": "Instant-speed buyback spells during an opponent's upkeep will soft-lock them out of the game. Unfortunately, when they draw instant-speed removal, you get 2-for-1'd.  \n  \n![3](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=3&type=symbol)![White](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=W&type=symbol) [Anoint](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Anoint)  \n![3](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=3&type=symbol)![White](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=W&type=symbol) [Change of Heart](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Change of Heart)  \n![2](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=2&type=symbol)![Blue](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=U&type=symbol) [Whim of Volrath](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Whim of Volrath)  \n![3](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=3&type=symbol)![Blue](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=U&type=symbol) [Clockspinning](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Clockspinning)  \n![2](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=2&type=symbol)![Blue](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=U&type=symbol)![Blue](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=U&type=symbol) [Mind Games](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mind Games)  \n![4](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=4&type=symbol)![Black](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=B&type=symbol) [Imps' Taunt](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Imps' Taunt)  \n![1](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=1&type=symbol)![Red](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=R&type=symbol)![Red](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=R&type=symbol) [Ghitu Firebreathing](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ghitu Firebreathing)  \n![4](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=4&type=symbol)![Red](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=R&type=symbol) [Searing Touch](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Searing Touch)  \n![4](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=4&type=symbol)![Green](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=G&type=symbol) [Elvish Fury](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Elvish Fury)  \n  \n![1](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=1&type=symbol)![Blue](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=U&type=symbol) [View from Above](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=View from Above) + a ![White or Blue](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=WU&type=symbol) or ![White or Black](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=WB&type=symbol) permanent  \n![1](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=1&type=symbol)![Red](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=R&type=symbol) [Punishing Fire](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Punishing Fire) + [Grove of the Burnwillows](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Grove of the Burnwillows)  \n![1](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=1&type=symbol)![Black](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=B&type=symbol)![Red](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=R&type=symbol) [Death Spark](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Death Spark) + [Tortured Existence](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Tortured Existence)",
      "posted_by": "HuntingDrake",
